abstract: Software testing, and in particular, unit testing, is a crucial step in modern Data Engineering. Pytest and unittest are great tools for developing unit tests for PySpark applications. In this talk, I will provide code examples using both libraries. Also, I discuss the advantages and disadvantages that each of them brings.
